welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Woodmoor, a charming town known for its natural beauty and friendly community. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Butts AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at USAF Academy Airstrip Airport serves both civilian and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at USAF Academy Airstrip Airport is used exclusively for military flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but a valid military ID is required to access the network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Colorado Springs Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: West Terminal
terminals.description: The West Terminal at Colorado Springs Airport is primarily used for general aviation and private flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
